<h1>Help</h1>

<p>Lifecastor is an application for forecasting and simulating personal finance over life time:</p>

<ul>
<li><p>See the big pictures of your financial future under dynamic income, expense, and net wealth. </p></li>
<li><p>Analyze the impact of inflation, social security, and retirement age on your financial future. </p></li>
<li><p>Easy to modify input parameters allow you to run endless what-if simulations so that you can understand your financial future. </p></li>
<li><p>Statistically forecast your estate and wealth. </p></li>
<li><p>Display you simulated wealth paths into the future.</p></li>
</ul>

